# Gallery photos ARE committed and deployed with the site.
# Drop the 66 files listed in MANIFEST.txt into this folder, then
# `git add images/` — the image types below will be tracked.
#
# Ignore everything by default...
*
# ...but keep these:
!.gitignore
!MANIFEST.txt
!*.jpg
!*.JPG
!*.jpeg
!*.JPEG
!*.png
!*.PNG
